{"tid":1924964,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律政司内部和獨立法律意見均為唔告黎智英 鄭若驊親自「提點」：告佢會贏","createTime":"2020-03-14T04:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T05:10:04.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7967fa3d9f8cef9ca561640f903eb0242a69678","tid":1924964,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:49:11.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被指於2017年維園六四祈禱會，對長期跟蹤追訪他的《東方日報》記者揚言「我實搵人搞X你」，上月終被警方拘控刑事恐嚇。<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，律政司檢控人員和外間資深大律師的法律意見均不建議起訴，惟去年9月律政司司長鄭若驊親頒「御旨」，分析有合理勝算，建議檢控</span>。法律界人士指出，律政司司長一般不會過問此等尋常案件，司長親自給予意見，而且不同於內部和獨立意見，實屬罕有；有政界人士質疑是政治檢控。<br />\n<br />\n去年9月律政司給予進一步法律意見，由司長鄭若驊親自負責。<span style=\"color: red;\">據了解，鄭認為資深大律師未有適當地判斷「搞」字的威脅效果，客觀上黎智英確有威嚇行為和意圖，並非無意義怒罵，起訴有合理勝算</span>。警方取得意見後，相隔半年至今年2月底才拘控黎。 <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200314&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20880451\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200314%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20880451&d=B95HL5QQ1MLE%2FldfuzA7jzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=25b34dc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Fapple%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200314%26sec_id%3D4104%26s%3D0%26a%3D20880451&h=ae1d9728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/apple/a.php?i=20200314&amp;sec_id=4104&amp;s=0&amp;a=20880451</a>"},{"pid":"21e842f696ac30ef794bfa4351a4a5624ed1a3b2","tid":1924964,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ee2e198a30389e2797771d552ce86d50dc9504","tid":1924964,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91fb7afba70e58e7003e0b999e3a87fa5777031","tid":1924964,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"係咪真係有講都成問題"},{"pid":"287efca1a8b6dca42d5a81e57c981b32f27b4b26","tid":1924964,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3dfee24827085b8fd5944ceb5a8598547fdb7fb1","tid":1924964,"uid":36134,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"鄭日曄：有藍官幫拖，贏鳩硬，點解唔告？<br />\n除非佢地上訴到終審，咁都夠玩殘肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a705fcba087f9ae1efce6c987263fe83e6cc0e15","tid":1924964,"uid":68080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T05:10:04.000Z","msg":"肥佬黎仲唔同美國俾料<br />\n政治檢控證據"}]}